criteria.driver_alignment:
Represent — explicitly listed the formulas and metrics (OCF via tax shield, ICF, NPV, IRR, PI) forming the cash‑flow/evaluation framework;  
Implement — stated they ran the code in Colab and identified specific functions used (numpy NPV, IRR), showing application of the framework;  
Validate/Discover — reported validation checks, initial outlay and sensitivity results that tie the framework back to project decision.

Discover — framed the decision as both financial and strategic;  
Implement — executed quantitative analysis (code, NPV, IRR, sensitivity);  
Reflect — offered a strategic recommendation tying project to firm strategy.
